replies.author: 飞翔荷兰人
replies.txt_content: 还有乱码需要多往上面看一下，上面应该还有信息，因为你是从某个MOD缺失的信息开始截的，大多数错误信息都会从开始报错的第一句就说出是哪个插件或者MOD的问题，还会说出路径

replies.author: 飞翔荷兰人
replies.txt_content:
你需要设置多世界的出生点
我用的是MV就应该这样输入站在想设置的地方输入/mv setspawn，记住偏头的角度也会记录，就是你现在看到方向玩家复活也会看向那个地方

replies.txt_content:
报错信息这段很重要
[15:46:59] [Server thread/WARN]: **** SERVER IS RUNNING IN OFFLINE/INSECURE MODE!
[15:46:59] [Server thread/WARN]: The server will make no attempt to authenticate usernames. Beware.
[15:46:59] [Server thread/WARN]: While this makes the game possible to play without internet access, it also opens up the ability for hackers to connect with any username they choose.
[15:46:59] [Server thread/WARN]: To change this, set "online-mode" to "true" in the server.properties file.
这个服务器在不安全的模式下运行，这会增加黑客利用他的几率。
服务器没有开启玩家验证。
要改变这种状况，设置server.properties的“online-mode”为"true"
还有这个
[15:47:00] [Server thread/WARN]: Plugin `Adjure_Sings v1.1' uses the space-character (0x20) in its name `Adjure Sings' - this is discouraged

还有这个
[15:48:05] [Server thread/WARN]: java.lang.IllegalStateException: Unable to find method getTypeId ([]).
